Much belated, but I had an amazing time at Tampa Bay Comic Con! Thank you so much to everyone who came out, and thank you to @riotpressproductions for letting me hog a table corner, as well as @vaughncoleman for being a great table helper!

I don't think I've had so many great conversations about comics and creative life since college. It was inspirational and motivating. Looking forward to the next show!! ❤️

(Also, hail to the first IRL Creative Block meetup!)

#comiccon #tampa #tampabaycomiccon #comicsartist #artist #hellionarts #me

FIENDISH Chapter 2.5 "Survivor" is now live on Fund My Comic, and also available on fiendishcomic.com!
"Survivor" follows Kazimir as he struggles for purpose after the destruction of his hometown. This first standalone one-shot to the FIENDISH series is written by me, drawn by @mr_sketche5, and colored by @hyperwizart! Back it now to immerse yourself further in the world of Arvos!

🖤🖤🖤
